# Substack Article – Day 06

## Title:
The Rise of Evolution-Based Companions in BubuVerse

## Summary:
In this Substack post, I explore how Bubus in BubuVerse don't just evolve visually — they grow in intelligence, utility, and relationship with their owners. This evolution model aligns deeply with the long-term vision of a living metaverse.

